            . I am a Police-officer. I took the prisoner, and produce the property.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He touched me on the shoulder, and asked if I had found a handkerchief; I pulled out this, and asked if it was his. Mr. Raffle, of Long-alley, is my master.</p>
               <p>
            
